00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.740
 Delicious Recipes Cabbage Soup Recipe 

00:00:06.460 --> 00:00:09.980
 Wash 1 piece of cabbage and remove the stem parts. 

00:00:13.720 --> 00:00:17.660
 Cabbages are chopped as thinly as possible on the cutting board. 

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:30.680
 Chopped cabbages are placed in a suitable pot. 

00:00:33.720 --> 00:00:35.720
 Add 1 tablespoon of salt. 

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:39.840
 Add hot water and leave to scald. 

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:43.060
 Depending on the type of cabbage, the cooking time may vary. 

00:00:43.120 --> 00:00:47.000
 But for about 20 minutes, the cabbages are boiled until they are soft. 

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:51.180
 While boiling cabbage, 1 piece of onion is finely chopped 

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:55.100
 1 potato and 1 carrot are chopped into small cubes. 

00:00:55.740 --> 00:00:59.100
 2-3 tablespoons of oil is taken in a separate pot. 

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:04.380
 Onions are added and roasted until settled. 

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:11.660
 Chopped carrots added 

00:01:12.620 --> 00:01:14.880
 Stir for a few minutes with stirring. 

00:01:15.340 --> 00:01:17.340
 Potatoes are added. 

00:01:22.180 --> 00:01:24.800
 They are roasted together for a few more minutes. 

00:01:25.780 --> 00:01:28.940
 1 tablespoon of tomato paste is added and mixed. 

00:01:30.180 --> 00:01:31.280
 Paprika, 

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:32.680
 black pepper is added. 

00:01:35.060 --> 00:01:37.920
 Boiled and filtered broths are added. 

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:40.680
 Stirring is continued for a few minutes. 

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:49.300
 Add half a glass of fresh or frozen red bean. 

00:01:51.780 --> 00:01:53.780
 1 tablespoon of bulgur is added. 

00:01:54.980 --> 00:01:56.300
 The salt is adjusted. 

00:01:58.180 --> 00:02:00.460
 Stir by adding hot water. 

00:02:07.500 --> 00:02:13.220
 After boiling for 25-30 minutes until potatoes and carrots are allowed to cook until soft. 

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:16.600
 1 bowl of 2 tablespoons of corn flour is taken. 

00:02:18.860 --> 00:02:22.540
 Add half a glass of cold water and mix. 

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:29.000
 The corn flour mixture is added to the soup which is close to cooking. 

00:02:37.160 --> 00:02:39.380
 If the water is missing, the water is adjusted. 

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:42.320
 Cook for 5 minutes and remove from the stove. 

00:02:47.240 --> 00:02:51.660
 I suggest you try this recipe with different constructions in different regions of the Black Sea. 

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:53.100
 Enjoy your meal. 

